cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.RO 

This paper deals with computer vision and deep learning techniques to address video prediction. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new technique to overcome the limitation of spatial invariance in convolutional neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG and cs.AI). The paper also evaluates the effectiveness of the proposed method on two architectures, which involves neural networks and optimization techniques (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with video prediction, which is a task related to robotics and control (cs.RO).
